title: Easy Mumbai Spiced Beef & Freekeh Salad with Herby Yoghurt & Cashew-Peanut Mix
description: If you haven't tried freekeh, give this colourful bowl a try. Stirring fresh veggies and spinach through this
protein-rich ancient grain brings it to life, while the addition of succulent spiced beef strips delivers a nutritionally balanced meal everyone will love.

